  <description>
    <p>
      A simple RPG where you open doors and fight the monsters behind! They drop loot, you get stronger! You know the drill! Over 27 monsters, 64 items, crafts and stuff!
    </p> 
    <p>
      The game is based on the Omicron java game engine. Runs on Android, Linux, Windows and on the Browser.
    </p>     
    <p>
      The game audio was contributed by the following awesome persons: Sounds by: Juhani Junkala - Game Music by: RandomMind - Win Music by: Vincent Fasano
    </p>
